response = self.app.get('/%s/actors/%s/movies/%s' % (self.api, self.actors[
    0]['id'], self.movies[2]['id']), headers=self.headers)
self.assertEqual(response.status_code, 404)
response_json = json.loads(response.data or '{}')
self.assertDictContainsSubset({'message': u'Resource "%s" not found' % self
    .movies[2]['id']}, response_json)
